data.description: Convenient access to all Ludington has to offer. This 4 bedroom home offers a spacious, open floor plan on the main floor. The kitchen is large with plenty of countertop space and cupboards. Main floor primary bedroom and hardwood flooring throughout the living room and dining room. Features a 2 car detached garage and a full basement. The backyard is fenced and has several patio areas. Located near Copeyon City Park and local corner market. The park features a boat launch, fish cleaning station, and park for the kids. Just minutes from downtown and the City Beach. This home has so much to offer. Schedule your appointment today.
